%section{class: 'grid grid-cols-1 hero-height lg:grid-cols-2'}
  %div{class: 'bg-emerald-500 p-4 lg:border-r-2 lg:border-black'}
    .flex.flex-col.justify-center.items-center.w-ful.h-full
      .text-left.px-20
        %h1.text-4xl.font-bold.mb-10 Hey there, I'm Martin Yanchev!
        %p{class: 'text-2xl mb-5'}  A dedicated full-stack developer based in the city of Glasgow, Scotland.

        %p{class: 'text-2xl mb-10'}  I thoroughly enjoy architecting sophisticated web applications and immersing myself in various technological platforms, including Ruby, Python, Java, and Javascript.

        = link_to 'Check out my CV', '#', class: 'block bg-black p-5 text-white font-bold text-xl text-center mb-5 hover:bg-gray-800'
        = link_to 'More about me', '#', class: 'block bg-emerald-500 p-5 font-bold text-xl text-center border-4 border-black hover:bg-gray-800 hover:text-emerald-500'

  %div{class: 'bg-cyan-custom p-4 lg:border-l-2 lg:border-black'}
    .flex.flex-col.justify-center.items-center.w-ful.h-full
      = image_tag 'me.png'

%section.w-full.min-h-screen
  .bg-sky-600.py-20
    %h2.text-4xl.text-center.font-bold My Projects
  %div{class: 'bg-amber-500 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10 p-10'}
    - 6.times do
      .flex.flex-col.gap-5.bg-white.border-4.border-black

        = image_tag 'me.jpg', class: 'w-full max-h-64 object-cover'
        .p-5
          %h3.text-2xl.font-bold.mb-5 Project Title
          %p Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aliquam consectetur metus sed augue fermentum efficitur. Donec vel nulla metus. Phasellus varius, metus et posuere commodo, justo ipsum condimentum turpis, vel tempus orci augue id dolor. Donec facilisis quam arcu, sed molestie dui fermentum id.
        .flex.flex-col{class: 'w-full justify-between items-center border-t-4 border-black lg:pl-5 lg:flex-row'}
          = link_to 'See more ->', '#', class: 'block p-5 font-bold text-xl text-center border-b-4 border-black w-full lg:w-auto lg:border-r-4 lg:border-b-0'
          = link_to 'Github', '#', class: 'block flex-1 p-5 font-bold text-xl text-center'

